The thermal power plant of the Volga Automobile Plant was transferred to the T Plus energy holding. The construction companies JSC FGC Lada Dom, JSC Spetsstroy VAZ, JSC Avtozavodstroy and Avtovazbank were privatized. transferred to the FMBA of Russia. The KOP-VAZ Public Catering Plant was abolished; the property and the catering sector were transferred to the private CorpusGroup LLC[90] The factory VOKhR was abolished; security was transferred to a private Samara security organization OOO Avangard ChOO. Worker hostels were privatized and at the same time the housing and communal administration of the housing and communal services of VAZ was abolished, the Directorate for Capital Construction of the Office for the Capital Construction of Industrial Buildings and Structures PromUKS was abolished.